title: Grimm Fairy Tales 2013 Holiday Edition(2013)(Digital)(TLK-EMPIRE
description:
An annual Zenescope tradition returns with the 2013 Grimm Holiday Edition. This issue includes four new stories featuring some of your favorite characters from the Grimm Universe. Don't miss this issue and continue celebrating the holiday season in the usual Grimm fashion.
Story Titles

    A Very Robyn Hood Christmas
    The Reader
    Angel Atop the Tree
    Red Christmas
    Have Yourself Some Merry Little Krampi
